## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023, and some sources may have been published after this date, potentially affecting the timeliness of the information. Additionally, the scope of the search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant insights from non-English publications. The rapidly evolving nature of XR technology means that new developments could quickly alter the landscape described in this report.